    "Privacy policy and data collection practices for cureEDMD.": "cureEDMD 的隐私政策和数据收集实践。",
    "Registry outreach reminder": "登记处外展提醒",
    "Families can help research by joining registries when eligible.": "符合条件的家庭可以通过加入登记来帮助研究。",
    "Research partners": "研究伙伴",
