    "Patient and family photography placeholder": "患者和家庭摄影占位符",
    "Clinic and care team placeholder": "诊所和护理团队占位符",
    "cureEDMD was established in 2025. Before the foundation was formally launched, the founders had already been raising and directing funding for EDMD research for many years.": "cureEDMD 成立于 2025 年。在基金会正式成立之前，创始人多年来一直在为 EDMD 研究筹集和指导资金。",
    "We connect patients, families, clinicians, researchers, and drug developers so effective treatments can move faster.": "我们将患者、家庭、临床医生、研究人员和药物开发商联系起来，以便更快地开展有效的治疗。",
    "What we are solving": "我们正在解决什么",
    "EDMD is a genetic condition that can cause serious muscle weakness, joint stiffness, and dangerous heart complications.": "EDMD 是一种遗传性疾病，可导致严重的肌肉无力、关节僵硬和危险的心脏并发症。",
    "Why this matters": "为什么这很重要",
    "Families need better options now, and long-term research support to reach safer and more effective treatment pathways.": "家庭现在需要更好的选择和长期的研究支持，以找到更安全、更有效的治疗途径。",
