    "Year cureEDMD was officially established": "年cureEDMD正式成立",
    "Based on your team notes, founders Ray and Chris should be featured here with personal story content and family photos. This section is set up to make that update easy.": "根据您的团队笔记，创始人雷和克里斯应该在此处展示个人故事内容和家庭照片。设置此部分是为了使更新变得容易。",
