    "Founder portrait placeholder: Ray": "创始人肖像占位：Ray",
    "Founder portrait placeholder: Chris": "创始人肖像占位符：Chris",
    "Family story photo placeholder": "家庭故事照片占位符",
    "Emery-Dreifuss muscular dystrophy (EDMD) is a rare, progressive muscle disease. It was first described in the 1960s. EDMD is known for three common feature groups: joint stiffness, muscle weakness, and heart problems.": "埃默里-德莱福斯肌营养不良症 (EDMD) 是一种罕见的进行性肌肉疾病。它于 20 世纪 60 年代首次被描述。 EDMD 因三个常见特征组而闻名：关节僵硬、肌肉无力和心脏问题。",
    "Movement and muscle diagram": "运动和肌肉图",
    "Heart and monitoring graphic": "心脏和监测图形",
    "1. Joint stiffness": "1.关节僵硬",
    "Joint tightness often starts early, especially in elbows, heels, and neck/back.": "关节紧绷通常很早就开始出现，尤其是肘部、脚后跟和颈部/背部。",
    "2. Muscle weakness": "2、肌肉无力",
    "Weakness often begins in upper arms and lower legs and can slowly progress.": "无力通常从上臂和小腿开始，并且会缓慢进展。",
    "3. Heart involvement": "3.心脏受累",
    "Heart rhythm and conduction problems can be serious and may need urgent treatment.": "心律和传导问题可能很严重，可能需要紧急治疗。",
    "EDMD can be inherited in X-linked, autosomal dominant, or autosomal recessive patterns. The most common genes discussed on current source sites are EMD and LMNA.": "EDMD 可以以 X 连锁、常染色体显性或常染色体隐性模式遗传。当前源站点上讨论的最常见基因是 EMD 和 LMNA。",
    "X-linked": "X连锁",
    "Often linked to EMD variants. Usually affects males more directly, with female carriers at some risk.": "通常与 EMD 变体相关。通常对男性的影响更直接，女性携带者也有一定的风险。",
    "Autosomal dominant": "常染色体显性遗传",
    "Often linked to LMNA variants. One altered copy can be enough to cause disease.": "通常与 LMNA 变体相关。一份被改变的副本就足以引起疾病。",
    "Autosomal recessive": "常染色体隐性遗传",
    "Two altered copies are needed. Parents may be carriers without obvious symptoms.": "需要两份修改过的副本。父母可能是没有明显症状的携带者。",
    "Diagnosis": "诊断",
    "Diagnosis usually combines symptoms, exam findings, heart testing, and genetic testing.": "诊断通常结合症状、检查结果、心脏测试和基因测试。",
    "Heart follow-up": "心脏随访",
    "Ask how often ECG, Holter, and echocardiogram are needed for your situation.": "询问您的情况需要多久进行心电图、动态心电图和超声心动图检查。",
    "Daily management": "日常管理",
    "Discuss physical therapy, mobility supports, and emergency planning with your specialists.": "与您的专家讨论物理治疗、行动支持和应急计划。",
    "Symptoms appear": "出现症状",
    "Testing and diagnosis": "测试和诊断",
    "Care planning": "护理计划",
    "Long-term monitoring": "长期监测",
    "Based on cureEDMD source pages, current research focus is in two main areas: treatment-target discovery and gene therapy.": "基于cureEDMD源页面，当前的研究重点集中在两个主要领域：治疗靶点发现和基因治疗。",
    "Lab workspace placeholder": "实验室工作区占位符",
