    "Priority 1: Find useful treatment targets": "优先事项 1：找到有用的治疗目标",
    "Identify pathways in muscle and heart cells that might be treated with medicine. This includes checking whether existing FDA-approved medicines could help EDMD.": "确定肌肉和心脏细胞中可以用药物治疗的途径。这包括检查 FDA 批准的现有药物是否可以帮助治疗 EDMD。",
