    "When you visit our website, we may collect limited information including your IP address and how you interact with our pages. If you donate, volunteer, or join our registry, we collect contact information and details relevant to your involvement.": "当您访问我们的网站时，我们可能会收集有限的信息，包括您的 IP 地址以及您如何与我们的页面互动。如果您捐赠、志愿或加入我们的注册表，我们会收集与您的参与相关的联系信息和详细信息。",
    "We use information to:": "我们使用信息来：",
    "We implement reasonable security measures to protect personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.": "我们实施合理的安全措施来保护个人信息免遭未经授权的访问或披露。然而，没有一种互联网传输方法是完全安全的。",
    "You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. Contact us at info@cureEDMD.org to exercise these rights.": "您有权访问、更正或删除您的个人信息。请通过 info@cureEDMD.org 联系我们以行使这些权利。",
